Package: rEDM
Type: Package
Title: Applications of Empirical Dynamic Modeling from Time Series
Version: 0.6.14
Date: 2018-02-06
Maintainer: Hao Ye <hao.ye@weecology.org>
Author: Hao Ye [aut, cre],
    Adam Clark [aut],
    Ethan Deyle [aut],
    Steve Munch [aut],
    Jun Cai [ctb],
    Jane Cowles [ctb],
    Andrew Edwards [ctb],
    Oliver Keyes [ctb],
